                                                            </div>
                                                            <p class="vs-portfolio-heading-desccription">Teleport is Utah, USA based early stage startup. This is an marketplace app focusing on ever growing transport industry. It helps users to pick their product from one place and deliver to as per their choice. The users can post their requirement in a secs and choose the right driver for the job by checking their bids. It also offers secured OTP based deliveries to prevent any potential fraud.</p>

